latestIgtvVideos.title: She needs Pad
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Millions of women are devoid ofbasic needs. Indian brand everteen has come forward to help lockdown affected females by distributing 1 million free sanitary pads. 
Help us to help them in this tough situation by supporting this novel initiative of #SheNeedsPad • Go to www.SheNeedsPad.com and give the details of women whom you want to send free sanitary pad. • Create a similar video appeal and share it on your social media • Donate minimal amount so as to manage the delivery & logistic costs
Please share this post/video on your social media. Your one share can help a needy woman.
.
.
